{"tid":1508112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方：過去兩日施放過的催淚彈全部未過期 亦未派員喬裝示威者","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:51:34.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c05ff6768821b2cd78e405adca4fdbd8d8537e","tid":1508112,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"警方表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">過去兩日並無派員喬裝示威者</span>，又指全部被捕人士都是由防暴警察拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n被問到昨日有藍衣人追打示威者，警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥稱，當時有的士司機接載兩名乘客到二坡坊，因堵路問題與示威者爭執，有示威者濫用私刑圍毆，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方到場後發現的士尾箱有大量鐵通，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器拘捕司機和兩名乘客</span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於有指催淚彈生產日期被刮走，警務處助理處長麥展豪指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">過去兩日施放過的催淚彈全部未過期，強調催淚彈上的期限只是「最佳有效期」過後仍可使用，不會構成額外危險</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2230719/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2230719%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=58f342a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2230719/</a>"},{"pid":"ca5bbdf8c4ad7fd4691afcda5b9389f35bd35679","tid":1508112,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"劉業強啲招係咪比人拋棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2fb987c3b4da4bafb3a92874d1ab9ecf69838d","tid":1508112,"uid":156326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ca5bbdf8c4ad7fd4691afcda5b9389f35bd35679","tid":1508112,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"劉業強啲招係咪比人拋棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"梗係冇 佢講姐"},{"pid":"94426f0e090f95e2cfb8e1efb6bbac2367104a59","tid":1508112,"uid":74043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"哇好大恩惠啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/